Detailed Description

template<class T>
class gaia::base::HashSet< T >::iterator

Implements (non-const) iterator for hashset.

Hashset iterator is only used to traverse.

 // Creates a hashset and adds serveral datum.
 HashSet<size_t> hs;
 for (size_t i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
            hs.add(i);
 }
 
 // Creates an iterator for hashset.
 HashSet<size_t>::iterator iter;
 
 // Travese hashset
 size_t sum = 0;
 for (iter = hs.begin(); iter != hs.end(); iter++) {
            sum += *iter;
 }
